dictionary.description: Had he never received the order to assassinate the Oracle Maiden, Yuura likely would have continued his research into forbidden necromancy alongside Shida. Indeed, their inexhaustibly inquisitive minds might have discovered the source of the gods' power, and produced a technique for surpassing it. Had they done so, their research could have turned the tide in favor of the Bariura Empire in the great war that followed. Of course, this victory likely would have come at a great cost to humanity, albeit in a different form...
dictionary.evolution: Listen, because I'm only saying this once. I'm grateful to you for enhancing me to this extent. Thank you.
dictionary.fusion:
Yes, you have talent.
I won't say at what, though! Hahaha!
dictionary.summon: Heh, you can't get away from me. You see, I go after anything that I enjoy.
